snippet.title: Pyrene | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Defeat hellish monsters and rebuild your home in Pyrene, a fast paced roguelike dungeon-crawler game set in Basque mythology!

Play with different heroes & spells, collect powerful relics to upgrade your deck while uncovering the mysteries behind your village’s destruction.

Available now on Steam!

Link to store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2468100/Pyrene/

Developed by Two Tiny Dice
